file.name: multiPathParam.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenApi Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider

tags:
  - name: pets
    description: Pets Tag
  - name: list
    description: List Tag

paths:
  /pets/{petId}/petName/{petName}:
    get:
      summary: Info for a specific pet
      operationId: showPetById
      tags:
        - pets
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The id of the pet to retrieve
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: petName
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The id of the pet to retrieve
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Pets"
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        tag:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
    Dog:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Pet"
        - type: object
          properties:
            bark:
              type: boolean
    Pets:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Pet"
    Error:
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
